	<!-- Company Story -->
	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
				<div>
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="w-10 h-1 bg-accent mr-4"></div>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary font-heading">OUR STORY</h2>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darkgray mb-6">
						SERVING CENTRAL TEXAS SINCE 1993
					</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Founded in 1993, Alltek Services began with a simple mission: to provide honest, reliable, and high-quality
						HVAC services to the residents and businesses of Central Texas. What started as a small family operation has
						grown into one of the region's most trusted heating and cooling companies.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Our founder recognized a need in the community for an HVAC company that prioritized customer satisfaction
						above all else. Too often, homeowners and business owners were left frustrated by unreliable service,
						unclear pricing, and poor workmanship. Alltek Services was established to change that narrative.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Over the years, we've built our reputation on integrity, expertise, and exceptional customer care. We've
						grown not through aggressive marketing, but through word-of-mouth recommendations from satisfied customers
						who appreciate our honest approach and quality work.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-8">
						Today, we continue to uphold the values that guided us from the beginning. Every member of our team is
						committed to providing the highest level of service, ensuring that your comfort needs are met with
						professionalism and care.
					</p>
